{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"革命烈士诗抄  澧源歌","authors":["贺锦斋"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":21}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命烈士诗抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澧源歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺锦斋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澧源之水清且凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜿蜒漂荡入安乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸居民百余万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世代勤苦事农桑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大仓小廪堆谷米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有棉花运川康。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出产丰富衣食足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人鼓腹乐陶唐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那知好景难再得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群鬼怪恣妖孽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪官污吏与豪绅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此扭手相勾结。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽税筹款征钱粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催租逼押夺田宅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张三去了李四来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暮暮朝朝无停歇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新捐旧债紧纠缠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一窝青菜连根掘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门前鸡犬不闻声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶中烟火久断绝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜广大劳动人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难堪剥削与压迫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弃家逃走走无途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处乌鸦一般黑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底何处可藏身？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨天无梯地无穴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中忍受千般苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面面相对只悲咽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从南昌起了义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"澧源更招匪注意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认为贺龙生其间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定多革命潜伏力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惟恐烈火发高烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得蒋匪心着急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调遣大批强盗军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剿共溶共更积极。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫山遍野紧搜查，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬将人民当仇敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上套着红帽子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诬为犯了滔天罪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早到晚乱抓人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杀二绑三关闭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上鲜血流成渠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狱中冤囚挤破壁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多志士不怕死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿将肉身抗刀锯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尤有一事更痛心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婴儿也当纸撕碎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女不愿受奸污，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬梁投河甘自缢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼见浜澧八九县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山川改色人绝迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难实在比水深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲想排荡无良计。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾不断作斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结果总是败下去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常从事后追原因，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无人领导空叹息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家抬眼望贺龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有他能吞魔魅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党为人民谋解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须靠他作领队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党比父母恩德深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定不使民遭陷溺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然派他远归来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人雄心高百倍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐投入斗争场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不辞生死与艰巨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争可以求生存，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这点大家才明晰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此有党作领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们事事都不惧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我今写了澧源歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作一篇讨匪檄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋匪已经靠西山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂死挣扎也无济。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尚望万众一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力向前莫后退！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手执大刀和枪炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打遍湘鄂与赣豫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要将全国大片土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块一块来“割据”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前途障碍要荡平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭敌人要干脆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动统治要推翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民政权要建立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党如旭日向东升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光早已照大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民愤火化怒潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么力量难抵御！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命到处发吼声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"势如暴风卷残絮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"估计不到二十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定在京沪庆胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1928年"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"贺龙","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}